Looking ahead, the global IPTV market is expected to witness further expansion as new technologies such as 5G networks, artificial intelligence, and cloud-based streaming solutions continue to reshape the industry. These advancements are set to drive greater convergence between traditional television services and online streaming platforms, enabling users to access a wider range of content options through a single interface. Additionally, the proliferation of smart TVs, connected devices, and OTT platforms is expected to fuel the adoption of IPTV services among a broader audience, further accelerating market growth in the coming years.

